{"word":"G4741 - στηρίζω - stērízō - stay-rid'-zo - Fix","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στηρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>stērízō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>stay-rid'-zo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Fix"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஸ்திரப்படுத்து, திடப்படுத்து, நிலைநிறுத்து, உறுதிப்படு, உண்டாக்கப்படு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1. to make stable, place firmly, set fast, fix"},{"paragraph":"2. to strengthen, make firm"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2476 - ἵστημι - hístēmi - his'-tay-mee/2476\">G2476</a> (like <a href=\"#/G4731 - στερεός - stereós - ster-eh-os'/4731\">G4731</a>); to <i>set fast</i>, that is, (literally) to <i>turn resolutely</i> in a certain direction, or (figuratively) to <i>confirm:</i> - fix, (e-) stablish, stedfastly set, strengthen."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1991 - ἐπιστηρίζω - epistērízō - ep-ee-stay-rid'-zo/1991\">G1991</a>, <a href=\"#/G4740 - στηριγμός - stērigmós - stay-rig-mos'/4740\">G4740</a>, <a href=\"#/G4741 - στηρίζω - stērízō - stay-rid'-zo/4741\">G4741</a>, <a href=\"#/G793 - ἀστήρικτος - astḗriktos - as-tay'-rik-tos/793\">G793</a>"}]}